Billing daemon goals:

Account keeping
>> listen for modules data
>> session:
  >> get userID & value from module
  >> convert userID to account number  
  >> count money from value (and any other data)
  >> add/subtract money
  >> update account
  >> check account state
  >> enable/disable resource
  >> logging operations (each account)
  >> answer module (acknowlegement)

Log fields:
  >> Time/date
  >> Account no
  >> Money count (signed value)
  >> ModuleID (resource id)
  >> Resource count value
  >> User ID
  >> Protocol ID (ftp, http, etc.)  
  >> Host address (for dinamic IP or host-independed resource)
  >> Some additional data
